OL,3,CMartyn's Law backed by more than 100
OL,4,Cbusinesses
OL,6,FMore than 100 public venues - from
OL,7,FMcDonald's to the Slug and Lettuce -
OL,8,Fare backing the bill, ahead of its
OL,9,FSecond Reading in the House of Commons
OL,10,Ftoday.
OL,12,FIt is designed to improve public
OL,13,Fsafety by requiring all venues with a
OL,14,Fcapacity of over 200 to take simple
OL,15,Fsteps to ensure they have a plan in
OL,16,Fplace in case of an attack on their
OL,17,Fpremises.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
