OL,3,CMartyn's Law backed by more than 100
OL,4,Cbusinesses
OL,6,FMany of the 100 businesses which have
OL,7,Fsigned a letter in support of Martyn's
OL,8,FLaw are based in Manchester and
OL,9,Finvolved in the city-wide roll out of
OL,10,Fthe proposals ahead of the legislation
OL,11,Fbeing made law.
OL,13,FMartyn's Law was introduced to
OL,14,FParliament in September.
OL,16,FFigen Murray said: "The Second Reading
OL,17,Fof the Bill today is another huge step
OL,18,Ftowards delivering Martyn's Law.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
