OL,3,CMartyn's Law backed by more than 100
OL,4,Cbusinesses
OL,6,FJohn Shepherd, of Manchester music
OL,7,Fvenue, Band on the Wall said:
OL,8,F"Martyn's Law will make people safer -
OL,9,Fthat's the bottom line and that's why
OL,10,Fwe are delighted to support Figen
OL,11,FMurray and all those campaigning for
OL,12,Fchange.
OL,14,F"These are common sense changes to
OL,15,Fprotect our patrons and staff. Not
OL,16,Fonly do we support these changes -
OL,17,Fwe've already started to implement the
OL,18,Fnew rules.
OL,20,F"This is the right thing to do and we
OL,21,Fare proud to support Martyn's Law."
