OL,3,CMartyn's Law backed by more than 100
OL,4,Cbusinesses
OL,6,FNew regulations under the law could
OL,7,Faffect 155,000 smaller businesses with
OL,8,Fvenue capacity for between 200 and 799
OL,9,Fpeople, it is estimated, at an average
OL,10,Fanticipated cost of 330 pounds a year.
OL,12,FAround 24,000 larger venues, with
OL,13,Fcapacity of 800 and above, could be
OL,14,Fsubject to the laws and face average
OL,15,Fcosts of around 5,000 pounds a year as
OL,16,Fa result.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
