OL,3,CMartyn's Law backed by more than 100
OL,4,Cbusinesses
OL,6,FWhile the proposed laws will not apply
OL,7,Fto venues with a capacity of less than
OL,8,F200, business owners can choose
OL,9,Fvoluntarily to adopt measures and
OL,10,Ffollow guidance.
OL,12,FIt is not yet known when the rules
OL,13,Fcould come into force, if voted
OL,14,Fthrough by Parliament, but Government
OL,15,Fofficials anticipate it could take
OL,16,Fbetween one and two years for the Bill
OL,17,Fto become law and measures to be
OL,18,Fimplemented.
